eNCA Reporter Moloko Moloto is following the story for us POLOKWANE - The country's men and women in blue are being celebrated om Saturday. The SAPS is hosting an award ceremony to honour police officers and members of Community Policing Forums, who have gone beyond the call of duty to serve and protect. The Police top brass including minister Bheki Cele and Commissioner Fannie Masemola are attending the event. eNCA Reporter Moloko Moloto is following the story for us